plot: Nothing is what it seems when Gabriel surrenders himself to the lords of Vega.

Alex and Michael are at odds after the identity of a higher angel is revealed, forcing Alex to take his case to the Senate. After Claire and William marry, heeding his daughters' wishes, General Riesen departs Vega. Arika greets a delegation from Helena with shocking cargo in tow. Nothing is what it seems when Gabriel surrenders himself to the lords of Vega.—Anonymous
